@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tfslvo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v2 / wp.sin(v0 + 0.45)) / wp.exp(0.27))
    v1 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = wp.exp(0.35)
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.22 + tmp + 0.46) - v1) / v1)
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.92)) + wp.cos((v2 + 0.42 / tmp + 0.76)))
    data[tid] = v0
